# PinpointPizza
Pinpoint Pizza is a REST API built using the excellent [Dominos Node.js](https://www.npmjs.com/package/dominos) module by [@RIAEvangelist](https://github.com/RIAEvangelist).

This was created as a sample for an app built using WatchKit and the [SocialRadar](https://www.socialradar.com) SDK which would easily order a pizza to your current location.

# Group Stores
These methods are used to locate stores around you.

