## Store Info [/v1/stores/{store_id}]
Get detailed information about a given store

+ Parameters
    + store_id (required, string, `4233`) ... Numeric `id` of the Note to perform action with. Has example value.

### Retrieve a Note [GET]
+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Header

            X-My-Header: The Value

    + Body

            { "id": 2, "title": "Pick-up posters from post-office" }

### Remove a Note [DELETE]
+ Response 204
